'''Morten Veland''' was one of the founding members of the [[Norway|Norwegian]] [[gothic metal]] band [[Tristania (band)|Tristania]]. 

He was the main text composer/songwriter<ref>[http://www.sirenia.no/index.htm sirenia homepage]</ref>, and he was responsible for the [[death grunt|growling vocals]], and played guitar, untill he left tristania after the first two full length albums, because of social and musical differences<ref>[http://www.gothmetal.net/article/articleview/302/1/33/ gothmetal.net, tristania]</ref>.

After that he formed his own band [[Sirenia (band)|Sirenia]], creating the same genre of music, in which he contributes nearly all of the instruments as well as the growling vocals. The rest of the band are mostly used on live performences only.


== Discography ==
====with Tristania====
* ''[[Tristania (EP)|Tristania]]'' (Demo, 1997)
* ''[[Widow's Weeds]]'' (1998)
* ''[[Beyond the Veil (album)|Beyond the Veil]]'' (1999)

====with Sirenia====
* ''[[At Sixes and Sevens]]'' (2002)
* ''[[An Elixir For Existence]]'' (2004)
* ''[[Sirenian Shores]]'' (EP, 2004)
* ''[[My Mind's Eye]]'' (Single, 2007)
* ''[[Nine Destinies and a Downfall]]'' (2007)

